TopicTitle: KerbAir: Log of All Flights Over Kerbin

Articles.Content:
Welcome to my new mission report series! Here I will be posting a list of all flights to and from various locations (thanks in part by KerbalKonstructs). I will be using aircraft from my Hanger Thread which consists of aircrafts submitted by others! So enjoy  .

 

Flight Logs:

-

 

For the time being, there will be little activity as the hanger thread fills up, but once it has enough for us to begin flights, we will have something for just about every day! So check back often!
